title: Best of instrumental 3
description:
Best of instrumental 3 - 'Chosen Ones'

Hi again. Happy New Year and all that - and most of all, many thanks for the 600+ : 1 upload ratio for BOI2 I had just before creating this torrent :D I hope BOI3 will help me break that record :P
As usual, new files are in a separate folder, so you can easily download everything or just the new additions.

New in BOI3:
Anthony Ventura - 'Wind Of Change'

Chris Spheeris - 'The Arrow'
Cusco - 'Inca Bridges'

Coming up:
* The music of Stargate (I know it's overdue...)
* 1000 Anime Opening Themes - Part 1
* Best of instrumental 4 - 'New Hopes' (summer of 2009)
...and maybe more...
